WHERE runs BEFORE GROUP BY. You can't filter on aggregates in WHERE because the groups don't exist yet. You need HAVING, which runs AFTER GROUP BY.

SELECT department, COUNT(*) AS emp_count FROM employees GROUP BY department HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;

WHERE filters rows. HAVING filters groups. Tattoo this on your forearm.

